data.description: New construction by D.R. Horton! Welcome to the McKinley in Pleasant Valley. This 2-story home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, den, desirable open layout and 3 car garage and full walkout basement. Spacious great room is open to the breakfast nook and kitchen. Kitchen features cabinets with crown moulding, great storage, center island, beautiful quartz countertops and walk-in pantry. This home also features a built-in boot bench at entry 2 and spa-like bedroom and bathroom 1 retreat with double bowl vanity, tiled shower, private commode and walk-in closet. You will enjoy the storage of the walk-in closets in every bedroom. Enjoy relaxing outdoors on your deck. All D.R. Horton Indianapolis homes include our America’s Smart Home®.
